data.description: With quick access to major highways and less than 15mi from Downtown Dallas, this property sits in a prime location for its newest homeowners! This wonderful three bedroom home with a study sits on just under half an acre, tucked away in a sleepy neighborhood. Looking for upgrades? Check out the HUGE owner's suite with updated flooring, a remodeled bathroom with a jetted tub, and a large closet. Need more? From the kitchen boasting stainless steel appliances, to the granite countertops in the secondary bathrooms, and the backyard offering a covered patio overlooking plenty of yard space and trees, you have everything you can ask for. Call and schedule an appointment today!
